INSTALLATION:

1) Run 'configure' to generate the Makefile and conf.h.  Examine conf.h
	(especially) as well as Makefile to make sure configure set things
	up correctly.
2) Typing 'make' should be enough to build libmalloc.a and malloc_debug program
3) Typing 'make test' should build the malloc_test program

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

DOCUMENTATION:

Examine the malloc.info file.  Is is a gnu-info file having the
user-documentation for the malloc subsystem.  It is also suitable for reading
as text.

